"title": "6622: choice",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6622",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A deliberate act of will or decision, in which God chooses individuals or peoples to be his or calls them to perform certain tasks or responsibilities. Human beings are also required to make choices, particularly between good and evil.</p>\n<h2>God's sovereign choice</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:2-Mal1:3\">MAL 1:2–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:10-Rom9:15\">ROM 9:10–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:27-1Cor1:28\">1CO 1:27–1:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:5\">JAS 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's chosen people</h2>\n<h3>Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:4-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:4–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:2\">DEU 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:4\">PSA 65:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:1\">ISA 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:9\">ISA 41:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:14\">JER 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>NT believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4\">EPH 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28-Rom8:33\">ROM 8:28–8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>God chooses people for special tasks</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:10\">EXO 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:17\">1SA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:1-1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:1–16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:20-Hag2:23\">HAG 2:20–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:13-Mark3:19\">MRK 3:13–3:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:13-Luke6:16\">LUK 6:13–6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:15\">ACT 9:10–9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15-Gal1:16\">GAL 1:15–1:16</a></p>\n<h2>God chose where he was to be worshipped</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:5\">DEU 12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:11\">DEU 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:14\">DEU 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:18\">DEU 12:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:26\">DEU 12:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:23\">DEU 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:2\">DEU 16:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:6-Deut16:7\">DEU 16:6–16:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:11\">DEU 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut16:15-Deut16:16\">DEU 16:15–16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:2\">DEU 26:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:11\">DEU 31:11</a></p>\n<h2>People must choose between good and evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:15\">JOS 24:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">PRO 16:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:26\">EXO 32:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:19\">DEU 30:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:31\">PRO 3:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:10\">PRO 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:17\">JHN 7:17</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of bad choices</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:4\">JAS 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:28-Prov1:33\">PRO 1:28–1:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:12\">ISA 65:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:3-Isa66:4\">ISA 66:3–66:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:21\">MAT 27:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:9-Mark15:11\">MRK 15:9–15:11</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of wise choices</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:24-Heb11:26\">HEB 11:24–11:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:21-Josh24:24\">JOS 24:21–24:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:16\">RUT 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:5-1Kgs3:14\">1KI 3:5–3:14</a></p>",
